reviewText: I'm really disappointed at the quality of this disk! It's a total boot leg copy and not worth nothing! The sound is so rotten and wrong and the video sucks! Don't waist your money on this counterfeit crap!
The helicopter scenes were terrific.....did you know that David Janssen was a licensed pilot! I bet he did some, if not all, his own helicopter stunts.

The Movie being offered is the Re Cut Version,that does not Use, the Original
sound track,with Kay Kyser's 3 Little Fishies Song, and Music
